The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Good Morning

 Hello It's Sunday, May 27, 2007

 QUIZ time

 Take part in Mahaquizzer, a quiz competition, at Pragyananda Bhavan, 10am.

 Workshop

 Take your kids to a summer camp organised by Arunima Active at Bakulbagan Upper Primary School. 

 Join a workshop on Kathak, conducted by Sudeshna Moulik at EZCCs Bharatiyam Cultural Complex, 11am to 5pm. 

 Eye on art

 Browse through Connoisseurs Choice, a show of paintings at Genesis Art Gallery, noon to 7pm. 

 Drop in at Khela, works on paper, canvas and enamel by Arunima Choudhury, at Seagull Arts and Media Resource Centre, 2pm to 8pm. 

 Move on to Confluence, a painting exhibition presented by Reflection of Another Day, at Chitrakut Art Gallery, 3pm to 8pm.

 o through a painting exhibition at Angan Gallery, 2pm to 8pm. 

 Check out Park AD 2007, an exhibition of sculptures and paintings by Kirann Telkar at Bose Pacia, 11am to 7pm. 

 Take a look at paintings and sculpture by Behala Fine Arts Society at Birla Academy of Art and Culture, 4pm to 8pm. 

 Fair call

 Visit a furniture, Kitchen and Lifestyle Fair at Ice Skating Rink, 11am to 8pm.




